docs.lead_paragraph: NIBLO'S GARDEN.--The RAVELS came out with a Clean bill of health last night, and gave hearty pro. Raise of strength during the coming Summer. There was an entire change of performance-tight-rope, ballet, and pantomime. The last mentioned was the feature of the evening, and a very jovial one too.

headline.main: A Long Ganie of Deceit-The Extraordinary Brooklyn Case.

docs.lead_paragraph: We have already given in our columns a brief notice of a wonderful case of long undiscovered deception, practiced by a young woman in Brooklyn upon the pastor, officers, and members of a Method. ist Church in that city. Tho story, in all its details would be a longer one than our limited space for such romance would permit us to give, and only the outlines can be here presented.
